question: Which one among the following is in common with Arnold Schwarzenegger, Sigmund Freud, Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart, Niki Lauda; based on their nationalities?
option1: All of them were born in Austria
option2: All of them were born in Russia
option3: All of them were born in Spain
option4: All of them were born in Italy
answer: All of them were born in Austria
explanation: Adolf Hitler was actually Austrian. Famous personalities such as Arnold Schwarzenegger, Sigmund Freud, Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart, Christoph Waltz, Niki Lauda, Christian Doppler, Ernst Mach, Ludwig Van Beethoven were born in present-day Austria.
